@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<h2>World Cup Predictr</h2>

<h4>Predict the results of all the World Cup 2018 game to win prizes.</h4>
<a asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Sign up</a> to get started.

<h4>Rules</h4>

<p>Points are awarded as follows:</p>
<ul>
    <li>1 point for correct result</li>
    <li>3 point for correct score</li>
    <li>0 points for anything else</li>
    <li>Three Double cards can be played to double your points for a particular correct prediction</li>
    <li>Three Joker cards can be played to convert a correct result into a correct score. 
        Note, if this card is played and you get a correct score there is no bonus applied. 
        This card only converts a correct result of 1 point to a correct result of 3 points</li>
    <li>You can play a Double and a Joker card on the same match</li>
</ul>



